headline: GILD's Bictegravir and Lenacapavir Regimen for HIV Meets Primary Goal
summary: Gilead said its once-daily bictegravir/lenacapavir tablet met non-inferiority vs Biktarvy in phase III ARTISTRY-2, paving the way for filings.

headline: FDA ‘proactively’ hands J&J a voucher; Pfizer issues 2026 forecasts
summary: The FDA contacted J&J right after ASH to discuss using a special fast pass on a multiple myeloma regimen. Elsewhere, a new cell therapy player emerged and Sanofi cut deals with two startups.
